Actually, all the different terms are simply the venacular used to describe different arithmatic characteristics of particular dataset; any manipulation caused/generated with their (mis)use is totally up to the persuasive skills of the speaker. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
